<Placemark><name>DEP wetlands plus 200 ft buffer</name><description><![CDATA[<div style='font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:13px;'>MassDEP regulatory wetlands unioned with a 200-foot outward buffer, clipped to a 500-m envelope around Hampshire parcels. Treat the polygon edge as the outer extent of the regulated wetland envelope under a conservative reading of state and local rules.</div>]]></description><styleUrl>#wetEnvelopeStyle</styleUrl><MultiGeometry><Polygon><outerBoundaryIs><LinearRing><coordinates>-72.5510982,42.3126324,0 -72.5511156,42.3126061,0 -72.5511855,42.3125070,0 -72.5512050,42.3124811,0 -72.5512263,42.3124560,0 -72.5512494,42.3124319,0 -72.5512742,42.3124087,0 -72.5513007,42.3123865,0 -72.5513287,42.3123655,0 -72.5513405,42.3123570,0 -72.5514032,42.3123122,0 -72.5514321,42.3122926,0 -72.5514623,42.3122742,0 -72.5514939,42.3122569,0 -72.5515266,42.3122409,0 -72.5515604,42.3122263,0 -72.5515952,42.3122130,0 -72.5516309,42.3122010,0 -72.5516674,42.3121905,0 -72.5517046,42.3121815,0 -72.5517425,42.3121739,0 -72.5517807,42.3121678,0 -72.5518194,42.3121632,0 -72.5518584,42.3121602,0 -72.5518975,42.3121587,0 -72.5519366,42.3121587,0 -72.5519758,42.3121603,0 -72.5520147,42.3121634,0 -72.5520534,42.3121680,0 -72.5520916,42.3121741,0 -72.5521294,42.3121818,0 -72.5521666,42.3121909,0 -72.5522031,42.3122014,0 -72.5522388,42.3122134,0 -72.5522736,42.3122268,0 -72.5523074,42.3122415,0 -72.5523400,42.3122575,0 -72.5523715,42.3122748,0 -72.5524017,42.3122933,0 -72.5524306,42.3123129,0 -72.5524580,42.3123337,0 -72.5524839,42.3123555,0 -72.5525082,42.3123783,0 -72.5525309,42.3124020,0 -72.5525518,42.3124266,0 -72.5525709,42.3124519,0 -72.5525882,42.3124780,0 -72.5526036,42.3125047,0 -72.5526171,42.3125320,0 -72.5526286,42.3125598,0 -72.5526927,42.3127303,0 -72.5527020,42.3127576,0 -72.5527093,42.3127852,0 -72.5527148,42.3128130,0 -72.5527183,42.3128410,0 -72.5527198,42.3128691,0 -72.5527195,42.3128972,0 -72.5527172,42.3129253,0 -72.5527129,42.3129533,0 -72.55268